    q: 'What is the Delta executor?',
    a: "With the Roblox exploit called Delta Executor, which is sometimes referred to as a script executor, players may alter the game's environment in more intricate ways. Delta is a premium executor for Roblox exploits that you can get for free right now.",
  },
  {
    q: 'Is using Delta Executor safe?',
    a: 'Like with any other exploit, you will be banned from Roblox if you are found to be using it. But according to several users, Delta Executor performs a fantastic job eluding detection and restrictions.',
  },
  {
    q: "Why isn't Delta Executor working?",
    a: 'The Delta executor may not be functioning for a number of reasons, including as an outdated exploit, interference from antivirus software, an unsupported game version, injection issues, an exploit server problem, and several OS-related failures.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Which Roblox executor is best?',
    a: 'The ideal Roblox executor is the Delta E version, which is available for free here and will make updates simply accessible.',
  },
];

const jsonLd = [
  {
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'SoftwareApplication',
    name: 'Delta Executor',
    operatingSystem: 'Android, iOS',
    applicationCategory: 'GameApplication',
    offers: { '@type': 'Offer', price: '0', priceCurrency: 'USD' },
    softwareVersion: android.version,
  },
  {
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'FAQPage',
    mainEntity: faqs.map((f) => ({
      '@type': 'Question',
      name: f.q,
      acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: f.a },
    })),
  },
  getBreadcrumbSchema(Astro, [{ name: 'Home', path: '/' }]),
];
