        <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-text-muted">If the problem persists when attempting to insert your Delta exploit, make sure the executor's Pastebin is correctly checked and reinstalled. In the meanwhile, you may use Roblox Error Fixer to repair errors like these:</p>

        <ol class="mt-5 space-y-3.5 text-base text-text-muted">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-semibold text-accent">1</span> Start using the Delta exploit on your gadget.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-semibold text-accent">2</span> Navigate to the executor's settings and choose the "Delta Fixes" option. You may select "Install Dependencies" here.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-semibold text-accent">3</span> The message section's new page opens.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-semibold text-accent">4</span> The Roblox Error Fixer's "Start Fix" button should be selected. Press the "OK" button in the text section to proceed with your request.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-semibold text-accent">5</span> Allow the system to insert your Delta Executor into your device by turning on the extra steps.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-bg-card/40 px-6 py-16" id="faq-section">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold text-text">FAQs</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-3">
        {faqs.map((f) => (
          <details class="group card rounded-2xl p-5">
